    - All three render services now snapshot st_mtime_ns before transcode
      and re-stat after. If the source mutates during the build window, the
      service raises rather than os.replace'ing a stale-but-fresh-mtimed
      payload over a newer cache. Next request rebuilds against the newer
      source.
    
