      STL-only Viewport consumers save 11.29 KB gz; spec_v2 §AC#10 +50 KB
      delta budget preserved with margin.
    - parseGlbBytes is now async (was sync). Only caller (loadGlbFromUrl)
      was already inside an async function so no observable behavior change.
      Test updated to await both parseGlbBytes paths.
    
